data.description: Open concept 3 bedroom 3.5 bath home with 2 car garage and all the modern finishes. It features a mudroom off of the owner's entry, hardwood floors  throughout the entire main level, a flex room off the kitchen that could be used as an office or study, an upstairs loft for recreation and entertainment,  private en suites and large walk in closets in each bedroom. 2nd floor laundry. Chef's kitchen with a large granite island for entertaining overlooks the  great room and dining areas. Owner suite has a sitting area, dual vanity sinks, separate tub and shower and a large walk in closet. This home gets plenty  of sunlight and has a fenced backyard for privacy. Enjoy nearby Silver Comet Trail, 10 minute access to downtown Atlanta and the Battery at Suntrust  Park.
